io.kool.mongodb
Class ReplicaEvent

jet.Any
  io.kool.mongodb.ReplicaEvent


public class ReplicaEvent
extends Any

Represents an event in the MongoDb Replica Set
which is usually the oplog.rs collection in the local database
which is used to replicate changes to slave databases
